WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:18.730
Materials are the outer pouch fabric, 17cm by 45cm.
(Seam allowances are included)

00:00:19.200 --> 00:00:24.730
Pouch lining fabric, 17cm by 45cm.
(Seam allowances are included)

00:00:25.200 --> 00:00:30.730
2 cords (50cm).

00:00:37.200 --> 00:00:58.800
Lay the outer and lining fabrics with right side, and sew 3cm from edges.

00:00:59.330 --> 00:01:08.400
Press seam allowances open, and center the pouch mouth.

00:01:08.930 --> 00:01:24.730
Then sew the edges, leaving 6cm open and 2cm.

00:01:25.330 --> 00:01:34.600
Cut off extra cloth, and press seam allowances open.

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:44.470
Turn inside out, and iron.

00:01:44.930 --> 00:02:06.930
Insert the inner pouch into the outer pouch.
Then sew 2cm from pouch mouth.

00:02:07.530 --> 00:02:12.800
Sew the hem. (Ladder stitch)

00:02:13.330 --> 00:02:23.670
Thread the cord through, it's done.

